1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:29,960
Hello and welcome to the Self-Gravity Practice of our meditation program.

2
00:00:30,920 --> 00:00:43,480
That is strongly related to the sense of self and developing the internal

3
00:00:43,480 --> 00:01:01,280
presence. For this center of gravity plays as a crucial gateway to building this

4
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:06,520
internal self-presence.

5
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:35,800
Identify your precise location exactly where you are.

6
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:50,800
Let us trigger the practice by exhalation in a vertical, top-down fashion.

7
00:01:50,800 --> 00:02:06,040
Exhaled from your nose, from your chest, finish with exhaling from the belly and emptying

8
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:27,120
your body of air. Exhaled from the nose, from the chest, pull the belly in to push out

9
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:41,720
air, pull it in a little more, imp to yourself completely of air, then allow your body

10
00:02:41,720 --> 00:03:01,880
to breathing naturally. Shallow or deep as it wishes. Again, attention on the exhale from

11
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:21,920
the nose, from chest, from the belly, pull the lower belly in, push out the air, let your

12
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:45,880
body become empty of air. It can then easily inhale the air into your empty body.

13
00:03:45,880 --> 00:04:10,840
Exhaling downward from the top, from your chest, from the belly. No need to focus on inhaling

14
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:37,800
but the body breathing by itself. Again, from the nose, from chest, from the belly.

15
00:04:40,840 --> 00:05:09,800
Again, a vertical exhale, pull the belly in, push out the air.

16
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:36,760
Focus only on exhale, top-down, the vertical exhale.

17
00:05:36,760 --> 00:06:03,720
Next, exhale, bring your attention towards your chest area. Exhale all the way down.

18
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:27,720
Next, exhale, bring your mind lower to the abdominal area.

19
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:52,680
Exhale from the belly, bring your mind lower to the waist, lower to the belly.

20
00:06:58,200 --> 00:07:16,680
Exhale again, from the top, from the chest, from the belly and reach the point in your lower belly.

21
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:29,640
In the center, deep in the belly.

22
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:50,600
Use the exhalation to help you reach the point of gravity.

23
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:26,600
Reach the center of gravity.

24
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:43,560
Pull the belly in, push out the air and anchor in the center of gravity.

25
00:08:57,080 --> 00:09:13,560
Use your exhale to help you anchor in the point of gravity.

26
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:42,520
Reach the center of gravity.

27
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:59,480
It arises, shift your mind from thinking to center.

28
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:20,440
Back to center.

29
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:45,400
Now, observe your center of gravity.

30
00:10:45,400 --> 00:11:02,360
Let go of any breathing focus.

31
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:19,320
Go to the center, connect with the center of gravity.

32
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:36,280
Observe the center of gravity.

33
00:11:49,320 --> 00:12:16,280
From thought to center.

34
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:35,240
To the center.

35
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:52,200
Back to center.

36
00:12:52,200 --> 00:13:13,160
You may now raise your attention from the center upward towards the abdominal area.

37
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:30,120
Gently and slowly lifting up towards the chest.

38
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:51,080
Rising up to the center of the head.

39
00:13:52,040 --> 00:14:20,040
Come out through the ears and hear every sound.

40
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:41,000
The sound of anything you can hear.

41
00:14:51,000 --> 00:15:07,000
And slowly come back to the center of the head.

42
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:21,960
Lower to the throat, to the chest.

43
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:50,920
Down towards the center of gravity.

44
00:15:51,080 --> 00:16:07,880
The mind, connecting to the center of gravity.

45
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:24,840
Establishing the vertical link from the center of gravity.

46
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:41,800
To the center of head.

47
00:16:42,280 --> 00:17:06,760
The central link.

48
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:27,720
The vertical inner presence.

49
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:48,680
From the belly to the head.

50
00:17:49,640 --> 00:18:09,640
From point of gravity to the chest to throat to the center of head.

51
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:30,600
Stay in this inner presence.

52
00:18:39,640 --> 00:19:00,600
The inner vertical presence.

53
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:30,600
The home within.

54
00:19:39,640 --> 00:20:04,600
From lower center to the middle to the upper center.

55
00:20:05,560 --> 00:20:17,560
The vertical connection.

56
00:20:17,560 --> 00:20:30,520
Knot to the center.

57
00:20:47,560 --> 00:20:50,600
Let me climb up Mount Susvery and back.

58
00:20:50,600 --> 00:20:52,460
Hit once more.

59
00:20:52,460 --> 00:20:54,660
Move back to Mount Susvery home.

60
00:20:54,660 --> 00:20:54,820
Turn right and use your hands.

61
00:20:54,820 --> 00:20:57,060
Lead to Mount Susvery home.

62
00:20:57,060 --> 00:20:59,320
Move back to Mount Susvery home.

63
00:20:59,320 --> 00:21:01,320
Fold and tap over your lips.

64
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:01,760
Back to Mount Susvery home.

65
00:21:01,760 --> 00:21:03,520
So, this is...

66
00:21:03,520 --> 00:21:05,080
Front knee, back to Mount Susvery, back to Mount Susvery home.

67
00:21:05,080 --> 00:21:06,120
Turn right and use my hands.

68
00:21:06,120 --> 00:21:07,360
Turn back to Mount Susvery home.

69
00:21:07,360 --> 00:21:08,360
Turn back to Mount Susvery home.

70
00:21:08,360 --> 00:21:09,360
Turn back to Mount Susvery home.

71
00:21:09,360 --> 00:21:10,600
Turn back to Mount Susvery home.

72
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:11,000
Turn back to Mount Susvery home.

73
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:12,000
Turn back to Mount Susvery home.

74
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,880
Turn back to Mount Susvery home.

75
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:15,000
Turn back to Mount Susvery home.

76
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:15,800
Turn back to Mount Susvery home.

77
00:21:15,800 --> 00:21:17,040
Turn back to Mount Susvery home.

78
00:21:17,040 --> 00:21:24,040
.

79
00:21:24,040 --> 00:21:31,040
.

80
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:38,040
.

81
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:45,040
.

82
00:21:45,040 --> 00:22:10,040
.

83
00:22:10,540 --> 00:22:17,040
Cover your eyes with your palms.

84
00:22:28,040 --> 00:22:33,040
Cover your ears and hear yourself.

85
00:22:40,040 --> 00:22:47,040
Cover your ears with your palms.

86
00:22:47,040 --> 00:22:54,040
Cover your ears with your palms.

87
00:22:54,040 --> 00:23:02,040
Bring the palms in front of your eyes.

88
00:23:02,040 --> 00:23:09,040
Open your eyes.

89
00:23:09,040 --> 00:23:14,040
On your palms.

90
00:23:14,040 --> 00:23:20,040
The first thing you see is yourself.

91
